description:
The classic game of FreeCell, completely free!

This also includes a demo of Solitaire Collection.  Enjoy 15 deals of 9 of the most popular types of solitaire including Klondike, FreeCell, Yukon, Pyramid, Montana (Gaps), Spider, Canfield, Golf and Aces Up! Many variants are included as well, such as Spiderette, Spaces, Addiction, Russian Solitaire, Alaska, Westcliff and more. A total of 38 different games! This full featured game will provide endless entertainment. You can control the look and feel with custom backgrounds, and many other options. The game play is effortless with cards that are easy to drag, smart auto play and unlimited undo.
